data.description: Great entertaining home located in Lake Pointe Plantation and Veterans school district! This home features a master suite and a seperate suite upstairs. Bonus room off of the master bedroom, in-ground 18 x 36 Gunite pool with waterfall. Upstairs deck access from the master, oversees the pool. Downstairs there's a designated Office and half bath (set up for bedroom right now), 2 large living areas and an attached and detached garage on a .62 acre lot with a privacy fenced backyard!
